***Note**: [Comment](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-9575?focusedCommentId=17166732) by Neal Richardson (npr):*
`[~bkietz]` found the issue:

```Java

diff --git a/cpp/src/parquet/arrow/path_internal.cc b/cpp/src/parquet/arrow/path_internal.cc
index 8d2790aa0..89845867a 100644
--- a/cpp/src/parquet/arrow/path_internal.cc
+++ b/cpp/src/parquet/arrow/path_internal.cc
@@ -525,7 +525,7 @@ struct PathInfo {
   std::shared_ptr<Array> primitive_array;
   int16_t max_def_level = 0;
   int16_t max_rep_level = 0;
-  bool has_dictionary;
+  bool has_dictionary = false;
 };

 /// Contains logic for writing a single leaf node to parquet.
```

I'm working on reproducing the failure on crossbow so that we can prevent regressions, then I'll apply the patch.
